message.body: I think we should invest in some box wine for our party. To keep it classy
Want to do Andre champagne? It's $4 and even more classy ;)
Yesss let's do it
Are you going to go and get it tomorrow? I'll give you the money
I have some time tomorrow but I don't have a fake ID. All I can do is get a cake
I don't have a fake either....you get cake and I'll get party hats? Maybe Amit will make a run tomorrow?
Ok sounds good. I will ask someone who is going on a run
Perfect :)
OMFG HAPPY BIRTHDAY COME FIND ME SO I CAN GIVE YOU A HUG
I'm with the rents tonight but I'll see you tomorrow! Thank you
Nice ok have fun see ya!
Are we going to publix together or can you not make it?
I won't be back till noon but I'll be busy so I think we should just go separately. Anything else you want me to get?
Ok that's fine. I don't think we need anything else. There's plates and forks in the kitchen right? If we end up getting box wine instead of champagne I will pay for it
You sure? I'll split cost of cake with you of course
I don't want to get drunk tonight just by the way...I'd rather just have sober fun so I won't need any alcohol
Sounds good!
Oh ok. Then I just won't get any. And if I do you won't have to pay for it
Heading back to Dobbs with the cake. Can we store it in your fridge? If it doesn't fit we can put it in the fridge in the kitchen
Our door is locked but when I get back I'll take it from the downstairs kitchen
Ok. Since there's no alcohol we can host in the tv room or some common space. Also I'll be out with my family until like 9. Buuut I can't wait to see you!
Sounds great :)
Party at 10? I want to go to haunted Harris at 9
Ooooh what's haunted Harris? Sure 10 is good
It's like a haunted house. I'm so scared but might as well go
Lmfao have fun. Should I go around inviting people or should I post in the Dobbs group?
Dobbs group works
Aiiiight
HAPPY BIRTHDAY
Thank you! You were also the first to text me ❤
Yay
